        "creation_date": 1349317949,
        "body": "<p>Several things you should examine:<\/p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>if you have access to the server, is it logging anything?<\/li>\n<li><p>what content-types does the destination support?  You should probably specify the content type so the remote server knows what you are sending it:<\/p>\n\n<p>con.setRequestProperty(\"Content-Type\", \"text/html; charset=utf-8\");<\/p><\/li>\n<li><p>you may need to encode your text - look at Java's URLEncoder<\/p><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "answer_id": 12719552,
        "question_id": 12719106
    }],
